main event: A UFO report was filed which includes images of a street scene in Omaha, Nebraska on April 15, 1965.
interesting points: The cover page indicates that there are 2 photos associated with the report,The photographs depict a city street scene without visible human faces,One image shows a reflection in a puddle,The images are marked as unclassified and originate from the Foreign Technology Division,AFSC,No significant UFO activity was detailed in the descriptions of the images.
sighted object: city street with buildings and people
